{
  "page": "Knight of Oldstones",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>Knight of Oldstones</b> was a title held by Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Lymond_Fisher\" title=\"Lymond Fisher\">Lymond Fisher</a>, a knight of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Fisher\" title=\"House Fisher\">House Fisher</a> who rebelled against the rule of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Durrandon\" title=\"House Durrandon\">House Durrandon</a> and claimed the title of River King or <a href=\"/index.php/King_of_the_Trident\" title=\"King of the Trident\">King of the Trident</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_riverlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_riverlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Knight_of_Oldstones&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: See also\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Oldstones\" title=\"Oldstones\">Oldstones</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Fisher\" title=\"House Fisher\">House Fisher</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Knight_of_Oldstones&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_riverlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_riverlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7